CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 9, 1963, pg. 4, reads: "The Star! - Alberta Thompson was the star of the D.I. style show last Sunday night at Holiday House. The benefit show and dance aided the MENDS fund. - Harris Photo"
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Alberta Thompson wearing pinstriped skirt and button down suit jacket, and dark tall hat with band, standing in Holiday House for annual D. I. Club MENDS benefit
